flowchart TD
    Tool["Agent 调用 search_memory / zepSearch"] --> Target{"选择搜索目标"}
    Target -->|user_id| UserGraph["用户个人 graph<br/>适合偏好、历史、客户上下文"]
    Target -->|graph_id| SharedGraph["共享 graph<br/>适合文档、知识库、业务资料"]
    UserGraph --> Search["graph.search(query, scope, limit, filters)"]
    SharedGraph --> Search
    Search --> Scope{"scope"}
    Scope --> Edges["edges<br/>事实/关系，最常用"]
    Scope --> Nodes["nodes<br/>实体和 summary"]
    Scope --> Episodes["episodes<br/>原始 source data"]
    Scope --> Auto["auto<br/>Zep 组装 context string"]
    Edges --> Format["格式化成模型可读文本"]
    Nodes --> Format
    Episodes --> Format
    Auto --> Format
    Format --> Return["返回给 Agent<br/>作为工具结果或 context"]
